      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-eai-bone leading-tight">
        Risks
      </h1>
      <p class="font-serif italic text-eai-parchment/85 text-xl mt-3">
        The honest list of what could go wrong — and how each one is handled.
      </p>
